# Local agent/IDE context files. This repo is PUBLIC — a local CLAUDE.md (or
# .claude/ dir) carries per-host worker/project context and must never be
# committed. The orchestrator/worker ROLE is delivered at runtime by the
# SessionStart hook (orchestratia context-prompt), not by a committed file.
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
